class student{
    String name;
    Integer score;
    public student(String name, Integer score) {
        this.name = name;
        this.score = score;
    }
}

List<student> studentList = new ArrayList<>();

        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {  //处理输入
                studentList.add(new student(scanner.next(),scanner.nextInt()));//自动构造
            }

降序：    studentList.sort((o1,o2) -> o2.score - o1.score);

升序(默认升序)：  studentList.sort((o1,o2) -> o1.score - o2.score);